      "text": "We want to sell\nvarious flavored\nsoda that exist in\npopular mocktails\nwith many option\nsuch as sugar/no-\nsugar and\ncaffeinated/non-\ncaffeine\n\nWe also want our\nproduct to have\nless eco-footprint\nby offering recycle\noption for cashback\nor gift.",
