      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We want to sell various flavored soda that exist in popular mocktails with many option such as sugar/no-sugar and caffeinated/non-caffeine\n\nWe also want our product to have less eco-footprint by offering recycle option for cashback or gift.",
